{"tid":1590480,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"不要再說黃藍是政見","createTime":"2019-09-23T17:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-23T18:36:43.000Z","uid":11919,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"3abb42e9c5715b02c0eaa8a26721e786fe9777ce","tid":1590480,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"藍尸有三大罪狀<br />\n1. 支持恐怖組織赤納粹同黑警<br />\n2. 稱出去示威者為曱甴<br />\n3. 過去三個月內不斷使用暴力<br />\n<br />\n我認為佢地已經唔可以算係香港人，出賣良知同靈魂俾赤納粹，曲解自由既意思，用撕紙同暴力既手段去打壓香港人表達意見，以恐怖組織作為後台，明目張膽咁犯法再受到黑警包庇，不要再說黃藍是政見，藍尸如同魔鬼，係邪惡既代表，香港人係時候企出黎，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以武制暴，為民除害</span></span>。"},{"pid":"cf9b690b81bd6bfdf86d63be367632c194b6b0f4","tid":1590480,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:34:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YY8gJwH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYY8gJwH.jpg&h=de149ef0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n［行動］929細節出左了 唔該文宣 推爆佢 (2)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1589858\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1589858</a>"},{"pid":"9ec1c0ddcdf795568514ff0cc0ecc7570eb4647f","tid":1590480,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T17:42:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"93bf16821eb5518aa80f57e784cf185bde80ba6d","tid":1590480,"uid":11919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T18:36:43.000Z","msg":"推"}]}